+++++
Title: STXT Extras
+++++

= Contents ====================================================================

; stxt.css -- A basic stylesheet for displaying documents in STXT's native XML
              format.
; stxt.dtd -- A DTD for STXT's XML format. This is informative, stxt.xsd is
              normative.
; stxt.vim -- Adds STXT syntax highlighting to the Vim text editor.
; stxt.xsd -- An XML Schema for STXT's XML format. This is normative.
